            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ﴾: وأيُّ شَيءٍ أَعَلَمَكَ بِها؟</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "101:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ﴾: كالفَراشِ المُنْتَشِرِ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "101:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ﴾: كالصُّوفِ المُتَعَدِّدِ الألوانِ الَّذِي يُنْفَشُ باليدِ، فَيَصِيرُ هَباءً ويَزُولُ.</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "101:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ﴾: مَن رَجَحَتْ مَوَازِينُ حَسَناتِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "101:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ﴾: حياةٍ مُرْضِيَةٍ في الجنَّةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "101:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ﴾: مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَوَازِينُ حسناتِهِ وَرَجَحَتْ مَوَازينُ سَيِّئاتِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "101:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ﴾: فَمَأواهُ جَهَنَّمُ؛ لِأنَّهُ يَهْوِي فِيها عَلَى أُمِّ رَأْسِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "101:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ﴾: وأيُّ شَيءٍ أَعْلَمكَ؟</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَا هِيَهۡ﴾: ما هذهِ الهاوِيةُ؟</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "101:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
